org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi

Interface SqmMutationStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTableBasedMutationStrategy, CteBasedMutationStrategy, GlobalTemporaryTableStrategy, InlineMutationStrategy, LocalTemporaryTableStrategy, PersistentTableStrategy, SimpleSqmMutationStrategy

    public interface SqmMutationStrategy
    Pluggable strategy for defining how mutation (`UPDATE` or `DELETE`) queries should be handled. prepare(org.hibernate.Metamodel, org.hibernate.boot.spi.SessionFactoryOptions, org.hibernate.engine.jdbc.connections.spi.JdbcConnectionAccess) and release(org.hibernate.Metamodel, org.hibernate.engine.jdbc.connections.spi.JdbcConnectionAccess) allow the strategy to perform any one time preparation and cleanup. The heavy lifting is handled by the UpdateHandler and DeleteHandler delegates obtained via buildUpdateHandler(org.hibernate.query.sqm.tree.update.SqmUpdateStatement, org.hibernate.query.sqm.internal.DomainParameterXref, org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi.HandlerCreationContext) and buildDeleteHandler(org.hibernate.query.sqm.tree.delete.SqmDeleteStatement, org.hibernate.query.sqm.internal.DomainParameterXref, org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi.HandlerCreationContext) methods.
    "API Note:"
    See SqmMutationStrategyHelper.resolveStrategy(org.hibernate.boot.model.domain.EntityMappingHierarchy, org.hibernate.metamodel.model.domain.spi.EntityHierarchy, org.hibernate.boot.spi.SessionFactoryOptions, org.hibernate.service.ServiceRegistry) for standard resolution of the strategy to use. See also SqmMutationStrategyHelper.resolveDeleteHandler(org.hibernate.query.sqm.tree.delete.SqmDeleteStatement, org.hibernate.query.sqm.internal.DomainParameterXref, org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi.HandlerCreationContext, org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.internal.SqmMutationStrategyHelper.FallbackDeleteHandlerCreator) and SqmMutationStrategyHelper.resolveUpdateHandler(org.hibernate.query.sqm.tree.update.SqmUpdateStatement, org.hibernate.query.sqm.internal.DomainParameterXref, org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi.HandlerCreationContext, org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.internal.SqmMutationStrategyHelper.FallbackUpdateHandlerCreator) for standard resolution of the delete and update handler to use applying standard special-case handling
